RETENTION PERIOD
We will retain Personal Data for as long as the account is active. Where your account is inactive for a period of two (2) years , your account and its Personal Data will be deleted.
    Third parties with whom your data is shared for the purpose of providing the Services will keep your data in accordance with their own data retention policies.
CHANGES TO PRIVACY POLICY
Any changes we may make to our privacy policy in the future will be posted on this page and, where appropriate, notified to you by notifying you of a change when you next start the App or log onto the Website. The new terms may be displayed on-screen and you may be required to read and accept them to continue your use of the App or the Services.
CONTACT
Questions, comments and requests regarding this privacy policy are welcomed and should be addressed to
DPO@rya.org.uk
